{
  "stem": "979.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--told you, in the middle of the town, where my-- somebody I knew-- my-- my sister's grandmother lived around there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where they put us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't go in the main streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had already that-- the [NON-ENGLISH] they called them-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what they're called.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so you couldn't walk with that in the main streets and that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to go over there, to the other places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from there, then bit by bit, then, we would go by groups to the Baron Hirsch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the trains would be waiting there to go straight to Germany-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- but it took time here, because-- because there was many Jews there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which one?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's 151, which--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--we used to call it in Spanish, [SPANISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is what-- it was the name of the district.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was small little houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put us-- many people together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went-- we stayed with-- my brother had a violinist in the orchestra.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was 45 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was older, considering that we were very young, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had only one grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't have family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we went to live with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, the grandmother lived, I think there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we decided to go and live with her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And around there, everybody, there were all the Jewish people who had all the little houses that they were there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we couldn't go away from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no separation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if the-- if-- since you have this on you, you know, they-- if they see you walking in one of the other streets, you know, they'll punish you-- whatever they do, you know.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the troops?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
